var getCandidateLoginSession = function() {
if(zia.isCandidateLoginSessionRequestCompleted){

$L.ajax({
url: "/recruit/v2/chat-bot/cand-login-session", //no i18n
type: 'GET',//no i18n
async: false,
timeout: 30000,
success: function(response){
resolve(response);
}
})	
})
request.then(function(responseObj){
var candidateloginsession = responseObj['chat-bots'][0].details.candidateloginsession;
ziaChatBotData['CANDIDATE_LOGIN_SESSION'] = candidateloginsession=="" ? null : candidateloginsession;
zia.isCandidateLoginSessionRequestCompleted = true;
});
}
}

zia.minimizeChat=function(){

if($L("#input_cancelled_wrapper").css('visibility')=='hidden'){
ziaChatbotDiv.classList.remove('zia-chat-animation');//no i18n

}

'<h6>Closing the chatbot will stop the current conversation</h6>' +//no i18n
'<p>Do you want to close?</p>' +//no i18n
'<div class="zia-close-wrap">' +
'<a href="javascript:;" id="zia-chatbot-close-bot">Yes</a>' +//no i18n
'<a href="javascript:;" id="zia-chatbot-close-alert">No</a>' +//no i18n
'</div>' +
'</div>')[0]);//no i18n
$L('.cnd-chatbot-close-alert').addClass('fadeInBottom');//no i18n

$L('.cnd-chatbot-close-alert').removeClass('fadeInBottom');//no i18n

ziaChatbotDiv.classList.remove('zia-chat-animation');//no i18n
zia.toFooter();
});

zia.getOnBoardingSentences=function(sentences){
var customOnboardingSentences = [];
var sentence1 = {};
sentence1["id"]="1";//no i18n
sentence1["sentence"]="Find matching jobs";//no i18n
sentence1["actual_sentence"]="Find matching jobs";//no i18n
var sentence2 = {};
sentence2["id"]="2";//no i18n
sentence2["sentence"]="Register to portal";//no i18n
sentence2["actual_sentence"]="Register to portal";//no i18n
var sentence3 = {};
sentence3["id"]="2";//no i18n
sentence3["sentence"]="My applications";//no i18n
sentence3["actual_sentence"]="My applications";//no i18n
customOnboardingSentences[0] = sentence1;
var zrMainContainer = $L(zia.dataContainer); 

getCandidateLoginSession();

if(	!( ziaChatBotData['CANDIDATE_LOGIN_SESSION']!=null || ziaChatBotData['IS_CANDIDATE_LOGIN_ENABLED']!=true ) ){
customOnboardingSentences[customOnboardingSentences.length] = sentence2;
}
if(ziaChatBotData['CANDIDATE_LOGIN_SESSION']!=null && ziaChatBotData['IS_CANDIDATE_LOGIN_ENABLED']==true){
customOnboardingSentences[customOnboardingSentences.length] = sentence3;
}
return customOnboardingSentences;
}
zia.isOnboardingHookCalledForFirstTime = true;
zia.setOnBoarding=function(element,sentences,placeholders,hasHistory){
if(ziaChatBotData['IS_ABOUT_ENABLED']){
sentences.push("About company");
}
if(ziaChatBotData['IS_CONTACT_ENABLED']){
sentences.push("Contact details");
}
//Construct HTML and styles as per your need and push it to the element.
//var onBoardingContent = "Hello there! <br>I am "+ ziaChatBotData.botName+" Assistant. Im here to help you to apply a job opening to with "+ziaChatBotData.companyName+" easily!";//no i18n
//	var onBoardingContent = "Hello there! <br>I am "+ $ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTML(ziaChatBotData['BOT_NAME']) +". "+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTML(ziaChatBotData['WELCOME_MESSAGE']);//no i18n
var onBoardingContent = $ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTML(ziaChatBotData['WELCOME_MESSAGE']);//no i18n
var suggestedActions='';
var zrMainContainer =  $L(zia.dataContainer); 
for(var sentIndex=0; sentIndex<sentences.length;sentIndex++){
if(sentIndex==0){
suggestedActions+='<div class="ziaonboardinggetstartedbutton  proximal" style="margin-top:0%;margin-bottom: 5%;" data-sentence-index="0" onclick="ziaskills.sendMessage(this.innerText)">'+sentences[sentIndex]+'</div>';
}
else{
suggestedActions+='<div class="ziaonboardinggetstartedbutton  proximal" style="margin-top:10%;margin-bottom: 5%;" data-sentence-index="0" onclick="ziaskills.sendMessage(this.innerText)">'+sentences[sentIndex]+'</div>';
}
}
$L(element.children[0].children[0]).append($L('<div class="chatbotHomePage proxima"><div class="ziaonboardingdesc  proxima" onclick="sE();">'+onBoardingContent+'</div></div>')[0]	);
$L(suggestedActions).each((_,e) => $L(element.children[0].children[0]).append(e));
if(zia.isOnboardingHookCalledForFirstTime){
var chatPop = $L("zia-chat-bot .ziaChatPop");//no i18n
chatPop.addClass('zrc-ziachatpop');
$L(".askziaTit").text(ziaChatBotData['BOT_NAME']);//no i18n
$L(".zia_icons_zia_chatHeader").append($L("<span class='zia_icons_zia_chatavatar'></span>")[0]);//no i18n
$L(".chat-popup-onboarding")[0].prepend($L("<span class='bot-header-Illustration'></span>")[0]);
var onboardingButtonHTML = "";
var listOfOnBoardingButtons = $L(".ziaonboardinggetstartedbutton");//no i18n
listOfOnBoardingButtons.each(function(onboardingButtonIndex, onBoardingButton) {
onboardingButtonHTML+=onBoardingButton.outerHTML;
});
var modifiedOnboardingHTML = "<div class='zia-homepagebutton'>"+onboardingButtonHTML+"</div>";
var onboardingButtonsParent = $L(listOfOnBoardingButtons[0].parentElement);
$L(listOfOnBoardingButtons).each((_,el) => el.remove());
onboardingButtonsParent.append($L(modifiedOnboardingHTML)[0]);
$L("#invocationSentences").append($L('<div class="zia-main-menu"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>')[0]);//no i18n

}
else{

$L(".ziaChatPop_invocationSentenceWrapper").css('display','block');//no i18n
}

});

}
else{

}
});

zia.getClientSessionData=function(){
return zia.getClientSessionDataAsPromise();
} 
/* zia.getClientSessionData = function(){
//	var clientSessionData = {"isNewCareerSite":true,"domain":"priyacorp.localzohorecruit.com","pageid":"7339000006214027","page_name":"Careers","candidatelogin":"50cbfc892e65f131636d248ade67a2ae6f16e4c23df4f2feab70d237853e29121e1c09925f2a3c566d4b0acd9c05aef5"}

zia.getClientSessionDataAsJson=function(){
var customSessionData = {};
var zrMainContainer =  $L(zia.dataContainer); 
if(isOldCareerSite){
customSessionData.isNewCareerSite = false;
customSessionData.digest =  zrMainContainer.data("digest");//no i18n
/* if(ziaChatBotData['CANDIDATE_LOGIN_SESSION']!=null){
customSessionData.candidatelogin =  zrMainContainer.data("candidateloginsession");//no i18n
} */
}
else{
customSessionData.isNewCareerSite = true;
customSessionData.domain = document.location.hostname;
customSessionData.pageid = meta.page_id;
customSessionData.page_name = meta.page_name;
getCandidateLoginSession();
}
customSessionData.candidatelogin = ziaChatBotData['CANDIDATE_LOGIN_SESSION'];
return customSessionData;
}
zia.getClientSessionDataAsPromise=function(){
if(isOldCareerSite){
var customSessionData = {};
var zrMainContainer =  $L(zia.dataContainer); 
customSessionData.isNewCareerSite = false;
customSessionData.digest =  zrMainContainer.data("digest");//no i18n
customSessionData.candidatelogin = ziaChatBotData['CANDIDATE_LOGIN_SESSION'];
return customSessionData;
}
else{
var request = new Promise(function(resolve, reject) {
$L.ajax({
url: "/recruit/v2/chat-bot/cand-login-session", //no i18n
type: 'GET',//no i18n
async: false,
timeout: 30000,
success: function(response){
var customSessionData = {};
customSessionData.isNewCareerSite = true;
customSessionData.domain = document.location.hostname;
customSessionData.pageid = meta.page_id;
customSessionData.page_name = meta.page_name;
customSessionData.page_source = meta.page_source;
var candidateloginsession = response['chat-bots'][0].details.candidateloginsession;
ziaChatBotData['CANDIDATE_LOGIN_SESSION'] = candidateloginsession=="" ? null : candidateloginsession;
customSessionData.candidatelogin = ziaChatBotData['CANDIDATE_LOGIN_SESSION'];
resolve(customSessionData);
}
})	
})
return request;
}
}
zia.handleUpload=function(uploadObject){
if(resumeSupportedContentTypes.includes(uploadObject.file.type)){
var formData = new FormData();
formData.append("resume", uploadObject.file);//no i18n
var zrMainContainer =  $L(zia.dataContainer); 
var paramJSON = {};
paramJSON['career_site']=isOldCareerSite?"old":"new";//no i18n
//formData.append("isOldCareerSite",isOldCareerSite);//no i18n
if(isOldCareerSite){
paramJSON['digest']=zrMainContainer.data("digest");//no i18n
//formData.append("digest",zrMainContainer.data("digest"));//no i18n
}
else{
paramJSON['domain']=document.location.hostname;
paramJSON['pageid']=meta.page_id;
//formData.append("domain",document.location.hostname);//no i18n
//formData.append("pageid", meta.page_id);//no i18n
}
formData.append('careersite_details',JSON.stringify(paramJSON));//no i18n
var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
uploadObject.updateProgress(60,I18n.getMsg('crm.chatbot.attach.resume.parsing.alert'));
xhr.upload.onprogress = function (e) {
if (e.lengthComputable) {
uploadObject.updateProgress(80,I18n.getMsg('crm.chatbot.attach.resume.parsing.alert'));
}
}
xhr.onloadend = function (e) {
uploadObject.updateProgress(100,I18n.getMsg('crm.chatbot.attach.resume.parsing.alert'));
var responseObj = JSON.parse(e.target.responseText);
if(responseObj.status=="error"){
if(responseObj.code=="INVALID_DATA"){
uploadObject.onFailure(I18n.getMsg('zr.zia.cb.upload.file.invalid.type'));
}
else if(responseObj.code=="FILE_SIZE_MORE_THAN_ALLOWED_SIZE"){
uploadObject.onFailure(I18n.getMsg('zr.zia.cb.upload.file.size.exceeded'));
}else{
uploadObject.onFailure(I18n.getMsg('crm.migration.request.form.alert.failure'));
}
}
else{
uploadObject.uploadComplete(responseObj['resume'][0].details.id);
}
}
xhr.open("POST","/recruit/v2/public/chat_bot/resume");
xhr.withCredentials = true;
xhr.send(formData);
}
else{
uploadObject.onFailure(I18n.getMsg('zr.zia.cb.upload.file.invalid.type'));
}
}
zia.handlePrompt = function(functionName,data,element,responseHandled,fromHistory,fromPagination,param){
if(data.signupCandidatePortalSimple){ //not in use
element.innerHTML="<div class=\"showZiaMessage\"><span class=\"\"> <div><div class=\"zia_paragraph\">"+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTML(data.message)+"</div></div></span></div>";
$L(element.parentElement.parentElement).removeClass("noPaddingBotTxt");
if(data.firstTime){
RegisterCandidate.getRegisterForm();
}
data.firstTime = false;
return false;
}
else if(data.htmlContent && data.firstTime){ //not in use
data.firstTime = false;
var actualElementId = element.id;
element.id="firstMsg";
element.innerHTML="<div class=\"showZiaMessage\"><span class=\"\"> <div><div class=\"zia_paragraph\">"+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTML(data.firstMessage)+"</div></div></span></div>";
var firstElementDiv = document.createElement("div");
firstElementDiv.innerHTML= element.parentElement.parentElement.innerHTML;
element.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.appendChild(firstElementDiv);
element.id=actualElementId;
element.innerHTML=data.htmlContent;
var formFieldChildHTML= element.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.children[1].innerHTML;
var firstMsgChildHTML = element.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.children[2].innerHTML;
element.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.children[2].innerHTML=formFieldChildHTML;
element.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.children[1].innerHTML=firstMsgChildHTML;
return false;
}
else if(false && data.signupCandidatePortalSectionWise && data.firstTime){ //not in use
data.firstTime = false;
var actualElementId = element.id;
element.id="firstMsg";
element.innerHTML="<div class=\"showZiaMessage\"><span class=\"\"> <div><div class=\"zia_paragraph\">"+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTML(data.message)+"</div></div></span></div>";
var firstElementDiv = document.createElement("div");
firstElementDiv.classList.add("botSentText");//no i18n 
firstElementDiv.classList.add("noPaddingBotTxt");//no i18n
firstElementDiv.style.marginTop="15px";//no i18n
firstElementDiv.innerHTML= element.parentElement.parentElement.innerHTML;
element.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.appendChild(firstElementDiv);
element.id=actualElementId;
var portalSingupFormSelector = "#"+encodeURIComponent(data.uniqueId)+"_loadForm";
data.portalSingupFormSelector = portalSingupFormSelector;
data.htmlContent = '<div id="'+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTMLAttribute(data.uniqueId)+'_loadForm"><span class="zvoice-dot" style=" display: inline-block; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 3px; background: rgb(90,95,112,0.5); animation: wave 1.3s linear infinite;" ></span> <span class="zvoice-dot" style=" display: inline-block; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 3px; background: rgb(90,95,112,0.5); animation: wave 1.3s linear infinite;animation-delay: -1.1s;" ></span> <span class="zvoice-dot"  style=" display: inline-block; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 3px; background: rgb(90,95,112,0.5); animation: wave 1.3s linear infinite;animation-delay: -0.9s;" ></span></div>';
element.innerHTML=data.htmlContent;
var formFieldChildHTML= element.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.children[1].innerHTML;
var firstMsgChildHTML = element.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.children[2].innerHTML;
element.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.children[2].innerHTML=formFieldChildHTML;
element.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.children[1].innerHTML=firstMsgChildHTML;
RegisterCandidate.getRegisterForm(null, data);
return false;
}
else if(data.signupCandidatePortalSectionWise){
if(data.firstTime){
data.firstTime = false;
var actualElementId = element.id;
element.innerHTML="<div class=\"showZiaMessage\"><span class=\"\"> <div><div class=\"zia_paragraph\">"+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTML(data.message)+"</div></div></span></div>";
var firstElementDiv = document.createElement("div");
firstElementDiv.classList.add("botSentText");//no i18n 
firstElementDiv.classList.add("noPaddingBotTxt");//no i18n
firstElementDiv.style.marginTop="15px";//no i18n
firstElementDiv.innerHTML= element.parentElement.parentElement.innerHTML;
element.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.appendChild(firstElementDiv);
element.id=encodeURIComponent(data.uniqueId)+"_loadForm_1";
var portalSingupFormSelector = "#"+encodeURIComponent(data.uniqueId)+"_loadForm";
data.portalSingupFormSelector = portalSingupFormSelector;
data.htmlContent = '<div id="'+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTMLAttribute(data.uniqueId)+'_loadForm"><span class="zvoice-dot" style=" display: inline-block; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 3px; background: rgb(90,95,112,0.5); animation: wave 1.3s linear infinite;" ></span> <span class="zvoice-dot" style=" display: inline-block; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 3px; background: rgb(90,95,112,0.5); animation: wave 1.3s linear infinite;animation-delay: -1.1s;" ></span> <span class="zvoice-dot"  style=" display: inline-block; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 3px; background: rgb(90,95,112,0.5); animation: wave 1.3s linear infinite;animation-delay: -0.9s;" ></span></div>';
element.innerHTML=data.htmlContent;
var formFieldChildHTML= element.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.children[1].innerHTML;
var firstMsgChildHTML = element.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.children[2].innerHTML;
element.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.children[2].innerHTML=formFieldChildHTML;
element.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.children[1].innerHTML=firstMsgChildHTML;
RegisterCandidate.getRegisterForm(null, data);
setTimeout(function(portalSingupFormSelector) {
$L(portalSingupFormSelector).parent().parent().parent().addClass('zia-bot-p0').addClass('zia-form-wrap');
$L(portalSingupFormSelector).parent().parent().addClass('max-inherit');
}, 100, portalSingupFormSelector);
return false;
}
else{
var formElenent = $L(data.portalSingupFormSelector)[0];
if(formElenent!==undefined){
formElenent.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.remove();
}
return false;
}
}
else if(data.getChatbotPrivacyConsent){
if(data.firstTime){
data.firstTime = false;
Lyte.Component.render("chatbot-privacy-consent",data,"#"+element.id);
setTimeout(function() {
$L("#"+element.id).parent().parent().addClass('ziamatching-jobs');
$L("#"+element.id).parent().removeAttr('style');
}, 300);
}
return false;
}
else if(data.getCaptcha){
if(data.firstTime){
data.firstTime = false;
Lyte.Component.render("chatbot-captcha",data,"#"+element.id);
}
return false;
}
else if(data['renderType']=="zia-cb-match-job-list"){
document.getElementsByTagName("zia-chat-bot")[0].component.data.showActionSuggestions=false;
Lyte.Component.render("zia-cb-match-job-list",data,"#"+element.id);
setTimeout(function() {
$L("#"+element.id).parent().parent().addClass('ziamatching-jobs');
}, 300);
return false;
}
return true;
}

}
zia.isBotOpeningAutomatically = false;
}
},100);
},
zia.customReAlignSuggestions = function(t, e, a) {
var totalMessages = $L("div[class*='message_']").length;//no i18n
var returnNotZero  = false;
if(totalMessages!=1){
// zia skills code starts
if (!t)
t = document.getElementsByClassName("home-page-body-pseudo")[0];
if (a)
var i = a.getBoundingClientRect().height;
var n = document.getElementsByTagName("zia-chat-bot")[0].component.getData("chatMode") //no i18n
, o = document.getElementsByTagName("zia-chat-bot")[0].component.getData("actionNamespace")//no i18n
, s = document.getElementsByTagName("zia-chat-bot")[0].component.getData("actionId")//no i18n
, p = document.getElementsByTagName("zia-chat-bot")[0].component.getData("skillName");//no i18n
if ("popup" == n) {
var r = document.getElementsByClassName("home-page-footer")[0];
if ("suggestions" == e)
var l = document.querySelector("#suggestionsContainer .botSentContainer");//no i18n
else
l = document.querySelector("#clientSuggestionsContainer .botSentContainer")//no i18n
} else {
r = document.querySelector(".home-page-footer lyte-table"),//no i18n
l = document.getElementsByClassName("chat-suggestion-row")[0];
if (o || s || p) {
var d = document.getElementsByClassName("ziaComp-flip-card-inner")[0];
d && (d.style.transformStyle = "inherit")//no i18n
}
}
if (l) {
var c = r.getBoundingClientRect();
l.getBoundingClientRect();
l.style.width = c.width + "px";
var m = l.getBoundingClientRect().height + (i || 0);
l.style.left = c.left + "px";
l.style.top = c.top - m - 10 + "px";
t.style.height = "calc(100% - " + (m + 10) + "px)";
var returnNotZero = true;
}
// zia skills code ends
var suggContainer = document.getElementById("clientSuggestionsContainer");
var isVerticalAlign = false;
if(suggContainer!=undefined){
var suggestionsDiv = $L(suggContainer.firstElementChild);
if(suggestionsDiv!=undefined){
var firstSuggestionSpan = $L(suggestionsDiv.children()[0]);
if(firstSuggestionSpan!=undefined){
if(zia.vertialAlignSugg.contains(firstSuggestionSpan.text().trim())){
isVerticalAlign = true;
}
}
}
}
}
else{
var suggContainer = document.getElementById("clientSuggestionsContainer");
var suggestionsDiv = $L(suggContainer.firstElementChild);
suggestionsDiv.css({'margin-left':'50px !important'});//no i18n
var firstSuggestionSpan = $L(suggestionsDiv.children()[0]);
firstSuggestionSpan.css({'display':'table'});///no i18n
var secondSuggestionSpan =  $L(suggestionsDiv.children()[1]);
secondSuggestionSpan.css({'margin-top':'3px'});//no i18n
}
var suggContainer = document.getElementById("clientSuggestionsContainer");
if(suggContainer==undefined){
suggContainer = document.getElementById("suggestionsContainer");
}
if(suggContainer!=undefined){
var suggestionsDiv = $L(suggContainer.firstElementChild);
if(suggestionsDiv!=undefined){
document.getElementsByTagName("zia-chat-bot")[0].component.scrollTop();
var newTop;
if($L($L("zia-chat-bot .ziaChatPop .botSentContainer.lastChild")[1]).offset().top==0){
//	newTop = Math.round($L($L("zia-chat-bot .ziaChatPop .botSentContainer.lastChild")[0]).offset().top + $L($L("zia-chat-bot .ziaChatPop .botSentContainer.lastChild")[0]).height()) + 15;
newTop = Math.round($L($L("zia-chat-bot .ziaChatPop .botSentContainer.lastChild")[0]).offset().top + $L($L("zia-chat-bot .ziaChatPop .botSentContainer.lastChild")[0]).height());
newTop = Math.round(newTop*1.05);
}
else{

zia.copyContactPhToClipBoard = function(){
var phElement = document.getElementById('cb-contact-ph');
var range = document.createRange();
range.selectNode(phElement);
window.getSelection().removeAllRanges(); // clear current selection
window.getSelection().addRange(range); // to select text
document.execCommand("copy");//no i18n
window.getSelection().removeAllRanges();// to deselect
$L("#cb-contact-ph-copied").css('display','block');//no i18n
$L("#cb-contact-ph-copy-to-clip").css('display','none');//no i18n
setTimeout(function() {
$L("#cb-contact-ph-copied").css('display','none');//no i18n
$L("#cb-contact-ph-copy-to-clip").css('display','block');//no i18n
}, 3000);
},
zia.handleResponse=function(functionName,data,element,responseHandled,fromHistory,fromPagination){
//do whatever you want to with the data and set it to the element which will appear in the chat area
if(data['secondMessage']){
if(data['followup_suggestions']){
setTimeout(function() {
ziaskills.pushTranscript({
message: data['secondMessage'],//no i18n
id: Date.now().toString(),
sender: "zia",//no i18n
status: "action_completion",//no i18n
display: !1,
show: !0,
time: Date.now().toString(),
followup_suggestions: data['followup_suggestions']
});
}, 300);
}
else{
setTimeout(function() {
ziaskills.pushTranscript({
message: data['secondMessage'],//no i18n
id: Date.now().toString(),
sender: "zia",//no i18n
status: "action_completion",//no i18n
display: !1,
show: !0,
time: Date.now().toString()
});
}, 300);
}
}
if(data['disableActionSuggestionsAndReturn']){
setTimeout(function() {
document.getElementsByTagName("zia-chat-bot")[0].component.data.showActionSuggestions=false;
}, 10000);
return true;
}
if(data['signupCandidatePortalSimple']){
RegisterCandidate.getRegisterForm();
return true;
}
if(data['showContactDetails']){
$L("#"+element.id).html('<div class="">'+
'<div>'+
'<div class="zia_paragraph">'+
'<div class="zia_header">You can reach us at..</div>'+//no i18n
'</div>'+
'<div class="zia_paragraph"></div>'+
(
data['phone']!=undefined 
?
'<div class="zia_paragraph zia-phone">'+
'<span  id="cb-contact-ph" class="zia-copywrap">'+
$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTML(data['phone'])+
'<span onclick="zia.copyContactPhToClipBoard()" class="copyclipicon" id="cb-contact-ph-copy-to-clip">'+
'</span>'+
'</span>'+
'<span class="zia-copyclip" style="display:none" id="cb-contact-ph-copied">'+
'Copied'+ //no i18n
'</span>'+
'</div>' 
: ''
)+ 
(
data['mail']!=undefined 
? 
'<div class="zia_paragraph zia-mail">'+
'<a href="mailto:?to='+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTMLAttribute(encodeURIComponent(data['mail']))+'" target="_blank">'+
$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTML(data['mail'])+
'</a>'+
'</div>' 
: ''
)+
(
data['website']!=undefined 
? 
data['website'].startsWith("https://") || data['website'].startsWith("http://") ? //no i18n 
'<div class="zia_paragraph zia-website">'+
'<a href="'+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTMLAttribute(data['website'])+'" target="_blank">'+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTML(data['website'])+
'</a>'+
'</div>' 
:
'<div class="zia_paragraph zia-website">'+
'<a href="https://'+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTMLAttribute(data['website'])+'" target="_blank">'+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTML(data['website'])+
'</a>'+
'</div>' 
: ''
)+
'</div>'+
'</div>');
return false;
}
if(data['showAnswerForScoldWithContactDetails']){
$L("#"+element.id).html('<div class="">'+
'<div>'+
'<div class="zia_paragraph">'+
'<div class="zia_header">'+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTML(data['topMessage'])+'</div>'+//no i18n
'</div><br>'+
'<div class="zia_paragraph"></div>'+
(
data['phone']!=undefined 
?
'<div class="zia_paragraph zia-phone">'+
'<span  id="cb-contact-ph" class="zia-copywrap">'+
$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTML(data['phone'])+
'<span onclick="zia.copyContactPhToClipBoard()" class="copyclipicon" id="cb-contact-ph-copy-to-clip">'+
'</span>'+
'</span>'+
'<span class="zia-copyclip" style="display:none" id="cb-contact-ph-copied">'+
'Copied'+ //no i18n
'</span>'+
'</div>' 
: ''
)+ 
(
data['mail']!=undefined 
? 
'<div class="zia_paragraph zia-mail">'+
'<a href="mailto:?to='+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTMLAttribute(encodeURIComponent(data['mail']))+'" target="_blank">'+
$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTML(data['mail'])+
'</a>'+
'</div>' 
: ''
)+
(
data['website']!=undefined 
? 
'<div class="zia_paragraph zia-website">'+
'<a href="https://'+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTMLAttribute(encodeURIComponent(data['website']))+'" target="_blank">'+$ESAPI.encoder().encodeForHTML(data['website'])+
'</a>'+
'</div>' 
: ''
)+
'</div>'+
'</div>');
return false;
}
if(data['renderType']=="zia-cb-match-job-list"){
document.getElementsByTagName("zia-chat-bot")[0].component.data.showActionSuggestions=false;
Lyte.Component.render("zia-cb-match-job-list",data,"#"+element.id);
setTimeout(function() {
$L("#"+element.id).parent().parent().addClass('ziamatching-jobs');
}, 300);
return false;
}
if(data['renderType']=="chatbot-job-list"){
Lyte.Component.render("chatbot-job-list",data,"#"+element.id);
setTimeout(function() {
$L("#"+element.id).parent().parent().addClass('ziamatching-jobs');
}, 300);
return false;
}
return true;
}
zia.isBotOpeningAutomatically = false;
zia.customTrigger = function(){
if(ziaChatBotData['TRIGGER_TYPE']=="1"){
var triggerWaitTime = parseInt(ziaChatBotData['TRIGGER_TIME']);
if(ziaChatBotData['TRIGGER_TIME_UNIT']=="Minutes"){
triggerWaitTime = triggerWaitTime * 60;
}
setTimeout(function() {
if(zia.loadingChatBotForFirstTime){
$L("#ziaChatbotDiv").css('visibility','hidden');//no i18n
zia.isBotOpeningAutomatically = true;
$L("#ziaChatBot").trigger('click');//no i18n
setTimeout(function() {
$L("#ziaChatbotDiv").addClass('zia-default-minheight');//no i18n
$L("#ziaChatbotDiv").css('visibility','visible');//no i18n
document.getElementsByTagName("zia-chat-bot")[0].component.scrollTop();
setTimeout(function() {
document.getElementsByTagName("zia-chat-bot")[0].component.scrollTop();
}, 100);
setTimeout(function() {
document.getElementsByTagName("zia-chat-bot")[0].component.scrollTop();
}, 200);
setTimeout(function() {
document.getElementsByTagName("zia-chat-bot")[0].component.scrollTop();
}, 300);
setTimeout(function() {
document.getElementsByTagName("zia-chat-bot")[0].component.scrollTop();
}, 400);
setTimeout(function() {
document.getElementsByTagName("zia-chat-bot")[0].component.scrollTop();
}, 500);
$L(".zrc-ziachatpop#ziaChatbotDiv.zia-default-minheight").click(function(event){//no i18n
if($L(".zrc-ziachatpop#ziaChatbotDiv.zia-default-minheight").length!=0){
$L("#ziaChatbotDiv").removeClass('zia-default-minheight');//no i18n
$L("#ziaChatbotDiv").addClass('zia-actual-height');//no i18n
event.stopPropagation();
}
});
$L(".zrc-ziachatpop#ziaChatbotDiv.zia-default-minheight #ziaComp_message_box").keydown(function(event){//no i18n
if($L(".zrc-ziachatpop#ziaChatbotDiv.zia-default-minheight").length!=0){
$L("#ziaChatbotDiv").removeClass('zia-default-minheight');//no i18n
$L("#ziaChatbotDiv").addClass('zia-actual-height');//no i18n
event.stopPropagation();
}
})
}, 100);
}
}, triggerWaitTime*1000);
}
else{
$L("#ziaChatbotDiv").addClass('zia-actual-height');//no i18n
$L("#ziaChatbotDiv").css("visibility", "hidden");//No I18N
}
}
zia.didConnect=function(){
zia.customTrigger();
}
zia.validateFormFieldsAndSubmit = function(tgt){
var formFieldValues = {};
var inputElements = $L('input[data-uniqueid="userinput-'+tgt.dataset.uniqueid+'"]')//no i18n
for(var i=0; i< inputElements.length; i++){
var inputElement = inputElements[i];
formFieldValues[inputElement.dataset.paramname]= inputElement.value;
}
ziaskills.sendMessage("Form Fields Submitted", JSON.stringify(formFieldValues));//no i18n
}
zia.setMessageData=function(action,param){
if(Object.keys(ziaMessageData).length>0){
return ziaMessageData;
}
